It's delicious.

51
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,260
I never knew you were so tacky.

52
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,280
Madam.

53
00:03:24,600 --> 00:03:25,680
I said

54
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,540
With you by my side,

55
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:30,280
this simple meal is also a delicacy.

56
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,520
Besides,

57
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,680
Besides, if we share a pair of chopsticks,

58
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,280
makes me feel sweet.

59
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,800
Yan Qiyuan, why are you so cheesy?

60
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:41,680
Is it?

61
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:45,320
