63
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,760
There's no joy without you

64
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,680
Let's go.

65
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:50,640
All right.

66
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,480
