72
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,250
I've never seen you so relaxed.

73
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:16,440
Eat more.

74
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,200
Shu Yan.

75
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,560
Is this the life you want?

76
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,280
Madam.

77
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,280
It's late.

78
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,610
It hurts my eyes.

79
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,610
The light is dim.

80
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,840
I'll embroider it tomorrow.

81
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,700
I've thought about it these days.

82
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:46,200
there's no love token between us.

83
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,080
So,

84
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:50,020
