88
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,440
I will do my best

89
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,560
to give you

90
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,770
in the world.

91
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,640
I trust you.

92
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,160
Let me out!

93
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:26,880
Let me out!

94
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,080
Shen Huizhi!

95
00:05:28,840 --> 00:05:31,080
You bitch! Let me out!

96
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,240
Then I'll wait to be a fisherman.

97
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,600
I'll get the door.

98
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:00,410
Who is it?

99
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,740
Stop knocking.

100
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:03,700
Coming.

101
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,720
