Order all the guards to gather now.

104
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,680
Why are you up?

105
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,760
I can't sleep.

106
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,160
What's wrong?

107
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,170
Nothing.

108
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,780
Alan, emergency call.

109
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,800
Let me have a look.

110
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,360
Soon.

111
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,400
What's wrong?

112
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,560
I don't know why.

113
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,730
I'm a little flustered.

114
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,840
Come back early. Be careful.

115
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,080
Got it, Mrs. Yan.

116
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,210
Don’t worry.

117
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,760
I haven’t found the answer Qi Qiu wants.

118
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,730
Wu Yinfang must be safe.

119
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:20,880
Madam.

120
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,720
Madam.

121
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:45,920
Madam.

122
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,090
Catch the murderer!

123
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:49,720
Mother!

124
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,480
Mother, what's wrong?

125
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,380
Uncle Erbai

126
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:55,880
How did you know

127
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,920
