128
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,400
You killed my mother.

129
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:00,600
Shu Yan.

130
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,640
I know you don't like Old Madam.

131
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,220
But you can't kill her.

132
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:05,960
I didn't.

133
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:06,800
Catch her!

134
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:07,970
I have evidence.

135
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,200
It's a letter from Madam.

136
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,000
I'm here to save someone.

137
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,320
I thought you wrote it yourself.

138
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:15,000
Get her!

139
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,760
Don't move.

140
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,760
I'll kill her if you come any closer.

141
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,420
Don't move.

142
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,760
I didn't expect you to use human lives as a trap.

143
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,760
