144
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,840
Shu Yan.

145
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:26,920
The same method doesn't work every time.

146
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:33,840
If you go soft at the critical moment, you'll lose the whole game.

147
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,160
Take him away.

148
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,480
You two!

149
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:39,560
Let go of me!

150
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:46,040
Get lost!

151
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,800
You unfilial son!

152
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,000
You want to release the murderer who killed your grandma?

153
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,400
Shu Yan won't kill anyone.

154
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:53,000
Grandma's death has nothing to do with her.

155
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:53,720
Uncle Erbai

156
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:55,520
Leave this to me.

157
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:01,440
I can help you.

158
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,640
I have evidence that my grandma committed suicide.

159
00:10:04,640 --> 00:10:06,300
It's Grandma's handwriting.

160
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,720
What do you want?

161
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,440
I never do a losing business.

162
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,360
I can let Shu Yan go,

163
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,680
but you have to do me a favour.

164
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,040
As long as I can save Shu Yan,

165
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,480
I'm willing to do anything.

166
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,880
I want you to remove the guard at North Gate.

167
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,440
