173
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,360
Wait for me.

174
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,560
I want to see Shu Yan safe.

175
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,760
Alert!

176
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,000
Hide.

177
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:01,920
Hurry up!

178
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,090
Beat him!

179
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,480
You asked me to open the city gate

180
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,880
